# Keep the Docker build context slim — faster uploads, smaller layers.
**/node_modules
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/.next
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/release
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
*.log
.DS_Store

# NOTE: apps/desktop is intentionally NOT excluded — apps/web's Vite build
# resolves shared component aliases against apps/desktop/src, so the web
# Docker build needs desktop source in its context. apps/api's Dockerfile
# only COPYs apps/api explicitly, so desktop source never lands in the
# API runtime image.

# Drizzle migration lock backups
packages/db/drizzle/meta/_journal.json.bak
